        </div>

        <div class="faq-list">
          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Who can participate in Ella Rises programs?</summary>
            <p>Our programs are designed for girls and young women ages 12-22. We serve students in middle school through college, with different programs tailored to each age group. We welcome participants from all backgrounds and communities.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How much do programs cost?</summary>
            <p>All Ella Rises programs are free for participants. We believe that cost should never be a barrier to accessing mentorship, education, and community support. Our programs are funded through donations and grants.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How do I become a mentor?</summary>
            <p>We're always looking for dedicated women to join our mentor team! Mentors must be 21 or older, commit to meeting with their mentee 2-4 times per month for one year, complete our training program, and pass a background check. <a href="/get-involved#mentor">Apply here</a>.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How are mentors and mentees matched?</summary>
            <p>We use a thoughtful matching process that considers shared interests, goals, personality, and location. Both mentors and mentees complete detailed profiles, and our team makes matches based on compatibility. We also allow both parties to meet before committing to ensure it's a good fit.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Can I volunteer without being a mentor?</summary>
            <p>Absolutely! We have many volunteer opportunities that don't require a year-long commitment. You can help with events, lead a workshop, provide professional services, or assist with administrative tasks. <a href="/get-involved#volunteer">Learn more about volunteering</a>.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How can my company get involved?</summary>
            <p>We partner with businesses in many ways: corporate sponsorships, employee volunteer programs, workplace giving campaigns, and more. <a href="/get-involved#partner">Contact us</a> to discuss partnership opportunities.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>Is my donation tax-deductible?</summary>
            <p>Yes! Ella Rises is a registered 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization. Your donation is tax-deductible to the extent allowed by law. You'll receive a receipt for your records after making a gift.</p>
          </details>

          <details class="faq-item">
            <summary>How do I enroll my daughter in a program?</summary>
            <p>Start by <a href="/contact">contacting us</a> or filling out an interest form. We'll reach out to discuss which program might be the best fit and walk you through the enrollment process. Space in some programs is limited, so we encourage you to apply early.</p>
          </details>
        </div>

